title: How to avoid phishing attempts. However it’s spelled, it’s bad news

media:group.media:title: How to avoid phishing attempts. However it’s spelled, it’s bad news
media:group.media:description: People hook fish with a metal hook and a lure, and scammers hook unsuspecting Internet users with an e-mail that seems unusually urgent or exciting. Learn about some of the tactics that scammers use to try to trick you into giving them personally identifiable information.
